name: Abdi Utan #3
description:
“ Aren’t we all trees? Unbelonged to a dying forest of a changing climate.  I’m waiting for the day I regenerate, regardless all things fail.  I am no forest without the rest.  I am no tree.  I am none?”  —— Lisan VI #27, A. Sebastianus . |

 For every edition purchased 1 Tree will be planted through Yagasu Foundation (Yayasan Gajah Sumatra), Indonesia.
